data.description: A Must See! Beautiful, Young 2021 Year Built, 4 Bedroom, 2 Bath, Pool and Spa Home with a 3 Car Garage and a Fenced Yard! Nice Entry Foyer. Great Room Floor Plan with Split Bedrooms. Lovely Kitchen with Granite Countertops, 36" Soft Closed Cabinets, Tile Backsplash, Nice Pull Out Cabinetry, and Walk In Size Pantry with Adjacent Bright Dining Area! Open Family Room with Pocket Sliders that lead to the Lanai and Pool. Fantastic Bright Main BR with Brand New Carpeting, Fan and Extra Large BR Closet. Ensuite Full Bath with Dual Sinks, Garden Tub, and Large Upgraded Shower. Three Other Good Size Bedrooms. Full Guest Bath Tub Shower Combo. Other Special Features Include: Lots of Recess Lighting, High Ceilings, Transom Windows, Several Tray Ceilings, Front Screened Entry, 4 Zone Irrigation System, 12x24 Tile thru out Main Areas, Carpet in BRs, Pest Tubes in Walls, Water Softener and Huge Garage. Large Laundry Room. Gorgeous Back Yard with Vaulted Screened Lanai, Heated Salt Water Inground Pool, Outdoor Shower, Extended Brick Patio Area, Above Ground Heated 6 Person Spa, Special Grassy Sunning Area Included, Palms, and 6 Foot Fenced Back Yard! Great Parking too Large Brick Paver Drive!
